_sText:
Extract the BSP file to your map directory.
C\Program Files(x86)\Steam\steamapps\(your steam name)\counterstrike source\cstrike\maps


Made with Source Sdk.
Technically, this map is in Beta, but to my knowledge, it's in a stable state at the moment so I may not have to do any sort of bug fixes. I may, in the future, add on to this map.


For questions or just to invite me to your server, here's my steam account: jeffmey
